manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

"com_bmr_desc_1" : "基础代谢率是指人体在静止状态下就会消耗的热量。基础代谢率越高，所消耗的热量也会越多，也就越不容易发胖。"
"com_bmr_desc_3" : "目前您的代谢水平太低，已达到喝水也会长胖级别：提高基础代谢率最有效的方式就是运动，每周至少慢跑一次，饭后开始走走路，提高身体代谢和消耗热量的能力吧"
"com_bmr_desc_4" : "目前您已达标，只要不多吃就可以轻松保持体重啦。保持基础代谢率最有效的方式是每天都进行一些低强度的运动啦，记得饭后走一走哟~"
"com_bone_biaozhun_desc" : "您的骨量水平标准。骨量在短期内不会出现明显的变化，您只要保持健康的饮食和适当的锻炼，就可以维持健康的骨量水平啦。"

"com_bone_buzu_desc" : "您的骨量水平偏低，这会导致腰酸背痛、驼背、易骨折等症状。注意控制酒精、咖啡和浓茶的摄入，这些都会加速骨头里钙质的流失。
 人体对钙的吸收率很低，您需要摄入更多钙含量较的高食物。长期以车代步、过度防晒也会造成骨量逐渐流失，每天午饭后可以步行10分钟，补充钙质又能保持身材~"
"com_bone_you_desc" : "您的骨量水平偏高，这说明您的生活习惯比较健康，营养摄入合理。由于骨量在短期内不会出现明显的变化，您只要保证健康的饮食和适当的锻炼，就可以维持稳定健康的骨量水平啦。"
"com_fat_desc1" : "身体单薄，脂肪率水平过低。在摄入足够蛋白质的情况下，请增加摄入一些高糖高热量的食物（如果汁、奶酪、动物肝脏等），有助身材健壮， 增强免疫力哦。"
"com_fat_desc2" : "脂肪率水平健康，注意保持摄入足够水分，增强代谢；饭后走一走，轻松保持脂肪水平不攀高~"
"com_fat_desc3" : "脂肪率水平在危险的区间，过高的脂肪率率不仅造成形体上的臃肿，更是各种慢性疾病的主要导火线，请立刻减少高油高热量食物摄入，从每日步行开始行动， 努力恢复到健康体重和好身材。"
"com_fat_desc4" : "脂肪率水平在非常危险的区间，过高的脂肪率不仅造成形体上的臃肿，更是各种慢性疾病的主要导火线，请立刻减少高油高热量食物摄入， 从每日步行开始行动，努力恢复到健康体重和好身材。"

"com_jirou_desc_1" : "肌肉是您身体消耗能量的主力军。增加肌肉量能让您更快地消耗热量，以最健康的方式减掉多余的脂肪和体重。
目前您的肌肉量偏低，蛋白质不足。主要原因是运动量过少和摄入营养不足。请从简单的饭后步行开始运动吧~"

"com_jirou_desc_2" : "肌肉是您身体消耗能量的主力军。增加肌肉量能让您更快地消耗热量，以最健康的方式减掉多余的脂肪和体重。
目前您的肌肉量在标准范围内，但蛋白质偏低，请继续保持适当的运动量，并加大膳食结构中蛋白质的比例。"

"com_jirou_desc_3" : "肌肉是您身体消耗能量的主力军。增加肌肉量能让您更快地消耗热量，以最健康的方式减掉多余的脂肪和体重。
目前您的肌肉量比较充足，请继续保持适当的运动量和和你的饮食。"

"com_vifat_biaozhun_desc" : "内脏脂肪指数反映您内脏脂肪堆积的程度。保持标准的内脏脂肪指数，可以大幅度降低您心脏病、高血压、高血脂和2型糖尿的发病风险。 
内脏脂肪水平正常，请继续保持健康的饮食和适当的运动！"

"com_vifat_jinti_desc" : "内脏脂肪指数反映您内脏脂肪堆积的程度。保持标准的内脏脂肪指数，可以大幅度降低您心脏病、高血压、高血脂和2型糖尿的发病风险。
 内脏脂肪水平偏高，要警惕脂肪肝、高血脂等疾病啦。请改变久坐不动、经常熬夜等不良生活和工作习惯，每天都能完成步行目标的话，一个月后内脏脂肪就会大大降低哦！"

"com_vifat_weixian_desc" : "内脏脂肪指数反映您内脏脂肪堆积的程度。保持标准的内脏脂肪指数，可以大幅度降低您心脏病、高血压、高血脂和2型糖尿的发病风险。
体型看起来正常，但内脏脂肪水平已经过高，很可能患有脂肪肝、高血脂等疾病，建议去医院诊查。请立即改变自己的饮食习惯，以少油清淡的食物为主；每天都能完成步行目标的话，一个月后内脏脂肪就会有所降低哦!"
"com_water_biaozhun_desc" : "身体循环比较正常，规律的饮食习惯和每天八杯水就可以维持正常的水分率水平啦。身体里充足的水分能帮助您更好地消化食物和吸收养分， 并促进代谢，带走废物和毒素。"
"com_water_buzu_desc" : "身体循环不畅，这标示着您的脂肪率水平很可能较高。请严格控制对高盐高脂肪食物的摄入量，同时增加运动量，身体里充足的水分能促进代谢， 带走废物和毒素。"
"com_water_you_desc" : "身体循环正常。身体里充足的水分能帮助您更好地消化和吸收养分，并促进代谢，带走废物和毒素。"

"com_weight_biaozhun_desc" : "体重相当健康，记得三餐要按时哦~
恭喜您~体重已经达到您设定的目标，注意保持哦！"
"com_weight_piandi_desc" : "您太瘦了，胃肠吸收不好的话一餐吃得多反而不能有效吸收，可以增加进餐次数"
"com_weight_piangao_desc" : "体重正在非常危险的区间，高血压、心脏病、糖尿病等代谢疾病的发病风险极高，请立刻减少高油高热量食物摄入，从每日步行开始行动，努力恢复到健康体重和好身材。"

"com_bmr_desc_3" : "at present your metabolic level is too low, the most effective way to improve basal metabolic rate is to exercise, jog at least once a week, start walking after meal, improve the body metabolism and the ability to burn calories."

"com_bmr_desc_4" : "now you have reached the target, as long as not eat more can easily maintain weight. The most effective way to keep the basal metabolic rate is to do some low-intensity exercise every day, remember to go for a walk after meals"

"com_bone_biaozhun_desc" : "Your bone mass level is standard. Bone mass will not change significantly in the short term, you can maintain healthy bone mass level as long as you maintain a healthy diet and proper exercise."

"com_bone_buzu_desc" : "Your bone mass level is low, this can cause backache, hunchback, easy fracture and other symptoms. Pay attention to control alcohol, coffee and tea intake, these will accelerate the bone calcium loss. The absorption rate of the human body to calcium is very low, you need to take more food with high calcium Level. Long-term car transport, excessive sun protection will also cause bone loss gradually, after lunch you can walk 10 minutes a day, which can create calcium by sunbath and can maintain the figure."

"com_bone_you_desc" : "Your bone mass level is high, which indicates that your living habits are healthy and your nutrition intake is reasonable. As bone mass does not change significantly in the short term, you can maintain a stable and healthy bone mass as long as you ensure a healthy diet and proper exercise."

"com_fat_desc1" : "Your body is thin and the body fat level is too low. In the case of adequate protein intake, please increase the intake of high sugar and high-calorie foods (such as juice, cheese, animal liver, etc.), can help build a strong, enhance immunity."
"com_fat_desc2" : "Your Body fat rate is in health condition, pay attention to maintain adequate water intake, enhance immunity; Take a walking after meal can keep you healthy"

"com_fat_desc3" : "Your body fat rate is in the dangerous level, excessive body fat rate not only lead to the body obesity, but also a variety of chronic diseases of the main fuse, please immediately reduce the high oil high calorie food intake, starting daily walk, try best to restore a healthy weight and good figure."

"com_fat_desc4" : "Your body fat rate is in the dangerous level, excessive body fat rate not only lead to the body obesity, but also a variety of chronic diseases of the main fuse, please immediately reduce the high oil high calorie food intake, starting daily walk, try best to restore a healthy weight and good figure."

"com_jirou_desc_1" : "Muscles are the main force in your body's energy consumption. Adding muscle energy allows you to burn calories faster and lose excess fat and weight in the healthiest way. At present your muscle mass is low, the protein is insufficient. The main reason is too little exercise and inadequate intake of nutrients. Please start with a simple walk."

playstore_details.title: M-Fitness
playstore_details.description:
Track your health and stay fit with M-Fitness!

This application allows you to easily monitor essential health and fitness data for: Body Weight, Body Fat Percentage, Body Water, Bone Mass, Muscle Mass, BMI, BMR and Visceral Fat. From the graph and chart displays, you can check changes in health trends. M-Fitness helps all our users stay on track for a healthier lifestyle.

Combine Bluetooth Body Composition Scale with Android devices, M-Fitness is invaluable. With lifting a finger, all your data will automatically recorded and are available under the application. And you can also store multiple users, such as family members and friends in your app, and keep track of their health status. Weigh yourself, M-Fitness will do the rest!

Feature Highlights:

1.Supports multiple users.
2.Exports data as TXT file.
3.Color diagram to make reading analysis a breeze.  
4.Includes standard data sheet for reference.
5.Zoom in for history in a particular hour, day, week, month or year.
6.Take a photo or choose a photo from your local album as your user portrait.
7.For a tutorial on how to use this app, you can visit: https://youtu.be/2UC9DBdkbQ0
